org.garret.perst

Interface IPersistentList<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Collection<E>, java.io.Externalizable, ILoadable, IPersistent, IStoreable, java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.List<E>, java.io.Serializable

    public interface IPersistentList<E>
extends IPersistent, java.util.List<E>
    Interface for ordered collection (sequence). The user can access elements by their integer index (position in the list), and search for elements in the list.
